- [x] Request latency histograms tracked automatically
- [x] Error rate counters tracked automatically
- [x] Structured JSON logging available (via LOG_FORMAT=json)
- [x] Request ID / correlation ID tracking in place
- [x] All services expose metrics (coordinator, blockchain, marketplace all have /metrics)
